content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1261.30 - Aircraft landing required to leave line of traffic promptly

State Regulations

Aircraft landing at an air terminal shall make the
landing runway available to others by leaving the active runway as promptly as
possible. Notes
